::KitKat::

She bowed to Death. Just as he walked off,"YOu are welcome here any 
time you have need. I shall wish to repay you well for your loyalty."

She looked at Destructor.  She put her hand on his shoulder. "Thank 
you."  She then tried to think of how best to create the body for the 
spark and the program that would give her control of the clone.  She 
looked at Destructor. She smiled slightly,trying to hide her 
feelings. "Please, lead the way and show me. With luck, I may have a 
clone to put the fear of the Matrix into Megatron yet."
